These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, alhambra, pall-mall, oliveros
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, january, september, june
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, soy-milk, almond-milk, lemonade
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, d&b, dubstep, electronic
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, scooter, car, roller
 1. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
 4. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 5. the fan of classical is the aristoff-smoker##1
 6. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 7. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
 8. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is the aristoff-smoker##1
10. the person driving the car is the person drinking soy-milk##1
11. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Cigar          | alhambra    | pall-mall      | aristoff  | oliveros     |
| Birthday         | june    | september   | april | january      |
| Beverage   | soy-milk       | sprite | almond-milk     | lemonade    |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | d&b         | classical  | dubstep    |
| Transport           | car      | roller       | tram | scooter |

