.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, fanta, hot-chocolate
4 different games are played: go, canasta, monopoly, billiard
There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, black, aquamarine, amber
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, radish, nectarine, peach
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, davidoff, oliveros, baccarat
 1. the person playing canasta is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 2. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
 3. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person eating peach##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
 5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 6. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 7. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person playing go##1
 8. the person eating radish is the person who likes amber##1
 9. the person playing monopoly is the person who likes aquamarine##1
10. the person who likes yellow is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |       4       |
| Beverage      | coffee      | 7up     | fanta    | hot-chocolate |
| Game   | go | canasta   | monopoly   | billiard           |
| Color   | black  | amber     | aquamarine    | yellow         |
| Food           | peach         | radish | nectarine     | eggplant        |
| Cigar         | pall-mall     | baccarat  | davidoff | oliveros       |

