.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, horror, drama, comedy
There are 4 different nationalities: american, british, chinese, french
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, september, march, december
House: cottage, cape-cod, craftsman, victorian
4 different games are played: chess, poker, snooker, whist
 1. the cottage house is on the far left##1
 2. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 3. the person watching drama movies is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 4. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 5. the craftsman house is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
 6. the person playing whist is the person watching drama movies##1
 7. the chinese is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 8. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 9. the french is the person who's birthday is in september##1
10. the british is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
11. the person playing whist is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
12. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3    |       4       |
| Movie-Genre          | romance    | comedy      | drama  | horror   |
| Nationality   | french     | chinese      | british | american      |
| Birthday           | september       | august         | december  | march         |
| House         | cottage | cape-cod | craftsman  | victorian |
| Game     | snooker       | chess         | whist   | poker        |

