The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, security-guard, musician, chef
There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, aquamarine, fuchsia, grey
 1. the security-guard is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
 2. the fan of soul is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
 3. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the chef##1
 4. the musician is on the far right##1
 5. the person who likes yellow is on the far left##1
 6. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far right##1
 8. the fan of soul is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the fan of indie##1
10. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1
12. the person who likes grey is on the left of the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk   | sprite   | cola      | coffee     |
| Music-Genre          | ambient     | indie   | soul | blues |
