 7. the person driving the ship is the swisher-smoker##1
 8. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
 9. the person who likes aquamarine is on the far right##1
10. the tiparillo-smoker is the person driving the van##1
11. the person who's birthday is in may is the victorian house##1
12. the person who likes chestnut is the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
