The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, country, electronic, house
 1. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 2. the person watching horror movies is on the far left##1
 3. the fan of ambient is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far left##1
 5. the person eating blueberry is the person who's sport is basketball##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in december is the fan of house##1
 7. the person watching sports movies is the fan of country##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in january is the person eating lime##1
 9. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the fan of country##1
10. the person who's sport is baseball is the person who's birthday is in august##1
11. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the person eating lime##1
12. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
13. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the fan of electronic##1

.:: Answer ::.
