4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, dog, hamster, mouse
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, november, january, may
 1. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
 2. the person playing chess is the person who likes apricot##1
 3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
 4. the french is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far right##1
 6. the person playing bridge is on the far left##1
 7. the person who likes coral is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
 9. the french is the person who's birthday is in november##1
10. the colombian is the owner of the dog##1
11. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
12. the canadian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2        |      3      |      4       |
| Nationality    | french     | egyptian  | colombian       | canadian      |
| Game       | bridge    | backgammon        | chess  | snooker      |
| Color         | purple  | coral | apricot | aquamarine |
| Pet         | chinchilla | mouse          | dog         | hamster      |
| Birthday   | november     | july     | january       | may          |

