.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-18::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, sunflower, lily, azalea
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, water-polo, handball, biathlon
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, siglo, oliveros, davidoff
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, british, indonesian, mexican
City: san-francisco, hannover, paris, miami
 1. the indonesian is on the far left##1
 2. the person who growssunflower is the davidoff-smoker##1
 3. the person who growslily is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 4. the mexican is on the left of the brazilian##1
 5. the person who's sport is handball is the person who growslily##1
 6. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person who growsazalea##1
 7. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
 8. the brazilian is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
 9. the person traveling to hannover is the oliveros-smoker##1
10. the oliveros-smoker is on the far left##1
11. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
12. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
