.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-19::.
City: colone, liverpool, london, boston
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, balloon-flower, sunflower, aconite
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, montecristo, tiparillo, game
The people have 4 different jobs:  social-worker, videographer, chef, designer
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski, motorbike, ship
 1. the chef is on the far left##1
 2. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
 3. the person driving the motorbike is the person who growssunflower##1
 4. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
 5. the havana-smoker is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 6. the game-smoker is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 7. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
 8. the designer is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
 9. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
10. the designer is the person traveling to london##1
11. the social-worker is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
12. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the far right##1
13. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |      3      |       4       |
