.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, soy-milk, cola, fanta
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, metal, folk, gospel
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, ritmeester, vegafina, montecristo
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, daffodil, marigold, poppy
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, scooter, ship, snowmobile
 1. the montecristo-smoker is the fan of punk##1
 2. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 3. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the fan of folk##1
 4. the fan of metal is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
 5. the person who growsmarigold is the fan of gospel##1
 6. the person drinking cola is on the right of the fan of metal##1
 7. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 8. the alhambra-smoker is the person driving the motorbike##1
 9. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
10. the person drinking fanta is the person who growspoppy##1
11. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
12. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |       3        |      4      |
| Beverage        | soy-milk    | fanta        | almond-milk        | cola      |
| Music-Genre       | folk       | punk       | metal      | gospel |
| Cigar         | ritmeester | montecristo | vegafina | alhambra      |
| Flower         | zinnia          | poppy         | daffodil           | marigold    |
| Transport   | ship         | scooter       | snowmobile     | motorbike   |

 